把咩咩屌打咩咩既POST啦 大撚把廢POST啦<br />\n接受唔到呢D文化死去過濾到打&quot;屌打&quot; 2隻字 包你唔會再見到呢D POST<br />\n入黎說教? 你D自信又邊到黎呀?<br />\n<br />\n我就好歡迎鐘意半澤直樹 覺得係神作入黎討論下<br />\n而唔係好似上面個2位咁 出黎就收皮泡撚 一係就仆街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163651a94a7be28333db3c1d00b8a1e0a9ac10f8","tid":2327592,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"但係堺雅人又係好正 好有魅力"},{"pid":"6eebdeba9747c12cbb9c0e3d73d1ee6315669f29","tid":2327592,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"163651a94a7be28333db3c1d00b8a1e0a9ac10f8","tid":2327592,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"但係堺雅人又係好正 好有魅力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"李狗嗨正d<br />\n感覺上職場上點會好似半澤直樹咁既浮誇表情動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef41aa3a9f284754e5fb21ad1658a8ca93f987c","tid":2327592,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eebdeba9747c12cbb9c0e3d73d1ee6315669f29","tid":2327592,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"163651a94a7be28333db3c1d00b8a1e0a9ac10f8","tid":2327592,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"但係堺雅人又係好正 好有魅力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"李狗嗨正d<br />\n感覺上職場上點會好似半澤直樹咁既浮誇表情動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"日劇係浮誇啲"},{"pid":"20e5716cf09d7714346ac629b83247d726005c6d","tid":2327592,"uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T22:47:19.000Z","msg":"班日劇能好嬲好嬲"}]}